<div class="eyebrow">What is Engage</div>
<h1>Job evaluation,<br/><em>rebuilt for modern organisations.</em></h1>
<p class="lead">Engage Job Evaluation is a modern factor-based methodology designed to help organisations evaluate roles in a way that is practical, transparent, and defensible — without bureaucracy, consultant dependency, or black-box scoring.</p>
